%% Рисунок 2 – Диаграмма последовательностей: путь от загрузки изображения до получения 3D-модели
%% Источник: diploma/text/04-architecture.md, секция 4.2
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as Пользователь<br/>(React SPA)
    participant A as Kotlin API
    participant S as MinIO (S3)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant K as Kafka
    participant W as ML Worker

    U->>A: POST /api/tasks (multipart image)
    A->>S: PUT input/{task_id}.png
    A->>DB: INSERT tasks (status=PENDING)
    A->>K: produce tasks-topic {task_id, s3_uri}
    A-->>U: 202 Accepted, task_id
    K->>W: consume tasks-topic
    W->>S: GET input/{task_id}.png
    W->>W: TripoSR inference (1.8 с на RTX 3060)
    W->>S: PUT output/{task_id}.glb
    W->>K: produce results-topic {task_id, status=DONE}
    K->>A: consume results-topic
    A->>DB: UPDATE tasks SET status=DONE
    U->>A: GET /api/tasks/{task_id} (poll)
    A->>DB: SELECT status, glb_uri
    A-->>U: 200 OK, presigned glb URL
    U->>S: GET presigned URL
    S-->>U: GLB-файл
